  ('commercial', 'Spectrum', '1100 Series Opaque Satin Glazes', '1121', 'Satin White', 'Cone 4 / Cone 6', 'Smooth satin finish on these stoneware glazes which are also lead free, A/P non-toxic and dinnerware safe', 'https://www.spectrumglazes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/1121.jpg'),
