  ('commercial', 'Speedball', 'Underglazes', '001034', 'Amethyst', 'Cone 05 / Cone 10', 'Speedball Underglazes have always been known for their superior value and for vibrant and consistent firing results, but in late 2023, we answered the call to adjust our formula to enhance brushability and delivered in a big way! Now the entire range of (48) colors features the same rich color palette in a smooth consistency perfect for any application, no modification required. Official product page notes the line fires from Cone 05 through Cone 10, is intermixable, and is dinnerware-safe when used and fired as directed.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-glqkoqulcz/images/stencil/1000w/attribute_rule_images/689_source_1774431955.jpg'),
